<example id="example" otherprops="examples"><title>Example</title><p>The following code sample shows preformatted text that contains white space and line breaks. When
            the following code sample is published, the white space and line breaks are
            preserved.</p><codeblock>&lt;pre&gt;
          MEMO: programming team fun day
Remember to bring a kite, softball glove, or other favorite
outdoor accessory to tomorrow's fun day outing at Zilker Park.
Volunteers needed for the dunking booth.
&lt;/pre&gt;</codeblock></example>
